  <h1 class="header-underline"> Muzit </h1>
  <section class="full-bleed project-details">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="col-3">
        <div>
          <h3>Overview</h3>
          <p>
            Muzit is a data analytics startup that monitors the global peer-to-peer (P2P) file sharing network of over 372 million households who have downloaded over 28 billion movies, music, video games, TV shows, software applications and other digital media. Muzit's platform enables client's to analyze category specifc torrent traffic, downloads and meta data to build targeted IP lists for direct advertising and marketing campaigns.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Role</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Design</li>
            <li>Rapid Prototyping</li>
            <li>Interaction Design</li>
            <li>QA Testing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Tech</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>HTML</li>
            <li>CSS</li>
            <li>SASS</li>
            <li>Bootstrap</li>
            <li>JQuery</li>
            <li>Jira</li>
            <li>GitHub</li>
            <li>Middleman</li>
            <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
            <li>AWS Elastic transcoder</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
