  <h2 class="text-center">Redesign</h2>
  <p>
    The design process started with creating a high-fildelity prototype using the Ruby based
    <%= link_to "Middleman", "https://middlemanapp.com", target: "_blank" %> static site generator to derive the page layouts and components. This method allowed me to quickly iterate on the designs and gave the team a very realistic representation of the design and functionality during the reviews. Furthermore the underlying HTML/CSS/SASS code could be implemented directly into the Rails application environment which saved development time.
  </p>
